      "edited" : false,
      "score" : 6,
      "creation_date" : 1618956969,
      "post_id" : 57957031,
      "comment_id" : 118758975,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I get this warning when <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-monitor/app/java-in-process-agent#quickstart\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">instrumenting my code with Azure Monitor Application Insights</a>, ie. when adding <code>-javaagent:path&#47;to&#47;applicationinsights-agent-3.0.3.jar</code> to my application&#39;s JVM args. Adding <code>-Xshare:off</code> gets rid of the warning (changing IntelliJ settings does NOT). Thanks!"
