      "comment_id" : 140363070,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Thank you for this tip, it was driving me crazy seeing this big red warning every time I ran any Java code in IntelliJ. I was not aware of the code folding option but that&#39;s a big help, you have saved my sanity and I don&#39;t need to disable any useful features"
    } ],
